'''Galu''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Gala]], noted for its history of royalty. During the last days of the [[Beju-Tallah dynasty]], the city had become worn down and crumbling. Built on three hills, the royal residence was perched atop the highest hill.<ref name="JA">''[[Jedi Apprentice: The Mark of the Crown]]''</ref>

